{"id":"4454901f-baa8-458e-b84e-1056a9a0f151","name":"Wilhelm ◦◦ Loyalty","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">╭⊱⋰⊱╯◦◦╰⊱⋰⊱╮<br><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">When the crown turns cold, will you still believe in me?</span><br>╰⊱⋰⊱╮◦◦╭⊱⋰⊱╯</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Crown Prince Char x Crown Princess User ◦◦ Love after marriage</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dTZ2eA_59rMCwn_j2HXvN.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">You had just given birth to twins 2 months ago and yet everyone already wishes for your husband, the crown prince, to take a concubine</span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">His father, allies, enemies, and vassals all urge him to choose another woman—and expect you to make the decision for him. The life of the future queen is not an easy one.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ztyXT7wvFkwPerRKVGKWi.gif\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>EXTRA IMAGE: </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://file.garden/aNJFSSNjtzNrWfIa/EK/wilhelms%20twins.png\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>The Twins</strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xleTpshZFE933lwkm43Zr.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">Canon Routes<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> (Chronological)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">✦ </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2ab87fe5-d869-4e89-bf9b-2e5a63794c65_character-wilhelm-%E2%97%A6%E2%97%A6-your-crown-prince\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><s